{"tid":2070810,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血時報2020書展詳情","createTime":"2020-06-19T11:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T13:08:30.000Z","uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d89861c9a10ba2d5fefa47b67a04bd3609cf17a9","tid":2070810,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OdiSSKX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOdiSSKX.jpg&h=5059e249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【熱血時報書展2020 簡易地圖教大家到HALL1B-B28】<br />\n<br />\n2020年書展將於7月15日灣仔會議展覽中心舉行，熱血時報今年亦會繼續參展，為大家帶來不同新著作。<br />\n為方便大家找到熱血時報展位，我們已準備地圖供大家參考。只要按地圖指示方向就可輕鬆找到。<br />\n有關2020年書展相關資訊，將於日後陸續更新，詳情請留意本專頁。<br />\n<br />\n熱血時報2020書展詳情：<br />\n日期：7月15日 至 7月21日<br />\n地點：灣仔會展HALL 1B-B28展位<br />\n<br />\n書展現場亦可為大家安排訂購PassionPrime，歡迎向在場同事查詢。"},{"pid":"482acc86f4f20ed830a2e61e5ae17e7749c5c7d7","tid":2070810,"uid":204475,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:27:37.000Z","msg":"法子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a163aa561093026c49daa4b70f0882391cb61b41","tid":2070810,"uid":73381,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:27:46.000Z","msg":"熱血公民 可以代表我 可以為我永續基本法<br />\n假使可以 五區當選<br />\n錦滿會打交 松泰負責投下反對票<br />\n這樣議事很足夠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6044cb5996bbd5a42c4d412b88b9bf30c11cc63a","tid":2070810,"uid":63095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"482acc86f4f20ed830a2e61e5ae17e7749c5c7d7","tid":2070810,"uid":204475,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:27:37.000Z","msg":"法子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:28:41.000Z","msg":"令人法子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":